                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18361024-3422-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18361024-3422-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18361024-3422-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>for a misdemeanour.</rs>
